N2  - In this article the author discusses his role as copy and production editor for the ?Academy of Management Journal.? The author notes that the main aspects of the job involve making sure that the authors' ideas are clearly and strongly expressed and to make sure that the publication is put out error-free and on time. He discusses the process that he goes through to make sure both of these goals are accomplished and discusses how the job has changed over the years.
